					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="5 Creative Link-Building Techniques For Your Website" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/1394153489-improving-seo-improving-links.jpg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
